Name: NOAA_GRID
Data_type: Regular grid based on multiple datasource
acquisition_date: Grid created in 1999, although datsats come from 1912 to 1991
Description: Various bathymetric data sources incorporated in a 70 meter resolution regular grid.  Data sources incorporated in this product and their footprint can be found at: https://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/mgg/greatlakes/lakeontario_cdrom/html/data_src.htm

Name: NONNA_10
acquisition_date: Data collection last update is in 2022. Although, datasets were collected from as far as 1912 to recent days
Description: Various bathymetric data sources incorporated in a 10-meter resolution product. When the original data resolution is coarser than 10m, there is no inteprolation, hence gaps remain in dataset. When original data is finer than 10m, dataset is resampled at a 10m resolution with seamless coverage. Original dataset footprints can be retreived by downloading data in CSAR format via https://data.chs-shc.ca/dashboard/map
